name: LAST LAUGH ipad cases
description:
IPADS
RINGHOLZ SPRING COLLECTION : 2013

10 new designs will be offered twice a year. 
Don't wait! 
This design might not be available in the Fall 2013 collection!

To accompany our popular phone covers, we are now 
offering the RINGHOLZ IPAD CASES for iPads 2/3/4

This is one of the best iPad cases you can find! 

Made of durable polycarbonate with a rubberized soft-touch coating, this full-body case features a magnetized smart cover design that protects your iPad during daily use. 

This is the only iPad case that offers all these features:

- Protect the iPad from all angles (front, back, all sides, and corners)
- Auto wake/sleep using Apple’s smart cover design
- Lightweight, thin profile, durable protection without adding bulk    
- Full access to all ports, buttons, and controls
- Multiple viewing angles: completely flat on the table, slightly tilted for typing, and at least three vertical angles for movie watching

Thank you all for your patience, but I wanted to give you the best product on the market and THIS IS IT, your iPad will snap right in!
Expect two weeks before delivery on ipads... sorry..

name: Assorted Postcard Set
description:
Enjoy 10 Ringholz postards and 5 envelopes to share with friends!
They are assorted, but should include bison/wolves/bears/elk/foxes and other western wildlife!  Fun to frame or send!

name: Dreamers Don't Sleep  Ringholz Book
description:
Dreamers Don't Sleep  Ringholz The First Ten Years 2002-2012
MY FIRST BOOK!!! is hot of the press!!!

An absolutely beautiful artistic journey through the first ten years of my work.  A 32 page full color (I mean FULL of color) soft cover book, that would be a treasure to artists, art lovers, collectors, wildlife lovers, lovers of Jackson Hole, and people who dig me.

They are hand signed and the first of many books to come... you've pretty much GOT to have one!

It may inspire your own dreams.....
You will adore it....

name: 2012 FAF Signed Poster FRAMED in black/alder/or barnwood
description:
Frame dimensions: 27 1/2" x 39 1/2" x 3/4"

Choose from: 

BLACK
A beautifully handcrafted wooden paint grade 
black frame which gives a contemporary look!

ALDER
A classic distressed Alder wooden frame.

BARNWOOD
A rustic look made from reclaimed Wyoming barnwood.

Holds the 36" x 24" Amy Ringholz HAND signed poster
for the 2012 Fall Arts Festival in Jackson Hole, Wyoming.

***Questions? Please email my framer, Scott Christiansen, 
at amyringholz.scott@yahoo.com.
